metadata.name: lock of drought
metadata.description:
"In times of drought and famine, it's not hunger that kills people, but the habitual fullness that kills them." It is my work of art that I designed with waste materials to protect nature and save our world from the garbage heap. In my artwork that I have physically designed; I use wood, metal and plastic materials. In short, by using waste materials, I give life to nature with art.
